          p Personal website and logo for Melissa De Leon, a Greater New York area independent filmmaker with experience in producing, writing, and being a production assistant. The site features galleries of her film and photography work, as well as her bio and professional contact information.  Give her a shout!
          p(md) You can view Melissa's site [here](http://melissadeleon.me).

      #mteach.page
        .img
